# Team Collaboration Problems

Software development teams often face collaboration challenges when proper workflows are not followed.

### Problem 1: Code Conflicts

Multiple developers may modify the same file at the same time.

### Solution

Use Git branches and pull requests.

---

### Problem 2: Deployment Errors

Manual deployments can introduce mistakes.

### Solution

Use Salesforce DX and automated deployment pipelines.

---

### Problem 3: Lack of Version Tracking

Without version control, teams may lose important code changes.

### Solution

Store all source code in GitHub repositories.

---

### Problem 4: Environment Differences

Developers may work in different environments, causing inconsistencies.

### Solution

Use Scratch Orgs for standardized development environments.

---

### Problem 5: Poor Communication

Changes made by one developer may not be visible to others.

### Solution

Use pull requests, code reviews, and documentation.

